-- CVC’s Sun Hung Kai Said to Plan Meetings With Bond Investors
-- B y   T a n y a   A n g e r e r
-- 2012-05-03T09:32:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/cvc-s-sun-hung-kai-said-to-plan-meetings-with-bond-investors-1-.html
Sun Hung Kai & Co. (86) , the Hong Kong-
based financial services company backed by CVC Capital Partners
Ltd., hired Standard Chartered Plc and UBS AG to help arrange
bond investor meetings in Hong Kong and Singapore, according to
a person familiar with the matter, who asked not to be
identified because the details are private.  Nancy Chen, Sun Hung Kai’s Hong Kong-based head of investor
relations, declined to comment on the sale when contacted by
phone today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tanya Angerer in Singapore at 
 tangerer@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
